":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T15:17:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老豆做三行做左三十幾年 期間做過老世<br />\n幾十年都係同一個班底<br />\n如果唔係識人 建築界好易開唔足工 因為無人授你玩</blockquote><br />\n你講既野咁似我個fd今日同我講既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e8930f87a0a02245ecb72964f5b3fd1e0243a0d","tid":301584,"uid":121131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T15:23:23.000Z","msg":"如果你係叻嘅師傅就實有野做<br />\n但白紙中工就要識下搵路數<br />\n如果你唔介意可試搵釘板周邊嘅工種做住先<br />\n例如上板搬板"},{"pid":"d0cfb3c39704abadf81bd91edd50a4f1f4cd640e","tid":301584,"uid":121131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T15:26:20.000Z","msg":"鋁板短期內唔能夠取代釘板<br />\n始終用木板彈性大好多, 隨時可以改"},{"pid":"487b6444b5e9cd4f2676f126fb33dc2f010bd359","tid":301584,"uid":125605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T00:40:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果你係叻嘅師傅就實有野做<br />\n但白紙中工就要識下搵路數<br />\n如果你唔介意可試搵釘板周邊嘅工種做住先<br />\n例如上板搬板</blockquote><br />\n佢而家連板都無得比我搬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7379a9ab03c723a2e8198d036a383a4bf372adf","tid":301584,"uid":125605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T00:42:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鋁板短期內唔能夠取代釘板<br />\n始終用木板彈性大好多, 隨時可以改</blockquote><br />\n都但而家咁既時勢，考多另一個牌好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有咩工種好介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}